&lt;p&gt;Duties/responsibilities include but are not limited to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Service&amp;nbsp;and configure Enterprise Level Access Control Systems, DDE Elevator Integrations, Enterprise LevelIP CCTV Systems, DVR’s &amp;amp; NVR’s, Burglar Alarms, Intercom systems, Telephone Entry Systems, and associated&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel to customer sites in company provided vehicle throughout Chicagoland Area, Southern Wisconsin, and Northwest Indiana.&lt;/li&gt;
