&lt;li&gt;Other duties as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education and/or Experience&lt;/strong&gt;: Associates Degree or Technical Degree.&amp;nbsp; Experienced in installing and programming Access Control systems.&lt;/p&gt;
