&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Other Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;: &amp;nbsp;Required skills include knowledge of computer networks, switches, IP addresses, routers, and modems.&amp;nbsp; Ability to pass pre-employment drug screen and criminal background check.&lt;/p&gt;
