&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wages &amp;amp; Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp; $30.00-50.00/hr (depending on experience) plus discretionary year-end bonus, paid vacation and personal days, medical insurance, dental insurance, vision&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;insurance, life and AD&amp;amp;D insurance, paid holidays, and 401(k) match.&amp;nbsp; Skills-enhancing training and opportunities for career growth and promotion.&lt;/p&gt;
