&lt;li&gt;Organize and maintain warehouse inventory, perform weekly cycle counts and assist with inventory audits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Material Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
