&lt;li&gt;Pull materials from stock and issue them to project jobs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure project materials are complete and available according to schedules.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shipping &amp;amp; Logistics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and package outbound shipments, process shipments using UPS shipping software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain shipping records and coordinate freight activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Purchasing Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with purchasing materials and equipment for projects.&

